{
  "stem": "19210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 208.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And you could very, very definitely see that showing in their-- in the-- in their punim, in their faces, so.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I understand, and I stand to be corrected as well, the World Zionist Organization had a lot to do with that, the American Joint Committee, the HIAS, the HIAS.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I believe that these were the main organizations which help with the funds, which they collected from other Jewish people to save Jewish lives.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they paid for the trips.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I must say that the food was excellent aboard the The conditions were pretty good.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Accommodations were pretty good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing that was not so good was the sea waves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were rough at times crossing the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We arrived in Israel, and here was a shocker really, again, perhaps the largest shocker to-- to-- more to the adults than-- than-- and to some children as well.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because the [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sochnut, ?] the-- the-- the Jewish Agency, naturally was waiting for us, as well as members of His Majesty's Government, the Palestine police, along with the Arab police, and along with Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They packed us into buses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They greeted us with halvah, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I ate so much halvah that I was sick for months because it was so good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it's-- it's something-- I do not know exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's made out of almonds and-- and lots of sugar, and it's-- it's like a candy bar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's so good that you just want to eat more and more and more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were not used to it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was the first time we came across halvah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we became sick, and not just me, most of our kids get-- got sick.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
